      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Should this put `blocks` into some quotes to clarify this is a string literal and not a English word (that e.g. can be translated). Thankfully we no longer translate those, but could still make it clear?\r\n\r\n```suggestion\r\n    gArgs.AddArg(\"-blocksdir=<dir>\", \"Specify 'blocks' directory (default: <datadir>)\", false, OptionsCategory::OPTIONS);\r\n```",
